quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  51,47,"N’amajuru twayagize k’ububasha bwacu, mu vy’ukuri ni twebwe bene ubushobozi bw’ibintu vyose"
  51,48,"N’Isi twarayishashe, rero abayishashe neza twebwe turi mu bantu beza gute"
  51,49,Mu vy’ukuri ibintu vyose twabiremye harimwo ikigabo n’ikigore kugira ngo mutegere neza
  51,50,"Rero\tni\tmwirukire\tku\tMana,\tjewe\tkuri\tmwebwe\tndi\tuwutuza k’umugaragaro mvuye iwe"
  51,51,"Kandi ntimugire uwundi kuba ariwe asengwa hamwe n’Imana, ntankeka jewe ndi mubatuza mboneka neza kuri mwebwe, kandi mvuye iwe"
  51,52,"Nuko rero nta ntumwa y’Imana iyariyo yose yashikiye abamyeho imbere yabo atari uko bavuga bati:- uyu n’umurozi canke n’umusazi"
  51,53,Mbega harico bapfana nibi bintu? Mugabo n’abantu babi cane
  51,54,"Ntaco ni mubareke gutyo nyene, na wewe ntuzo tabwako umwikomo"
  51,55,"N’ubandanye\tubibutsa,\tkuko\tuko\tkwibutsa\tkwawe\tniko\tkuzofasha abemera Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  51,56,Sinaremye ibisigo n’abantu mugabo n’uko bonsega
  51,57,"Sinkeneye kuribo imigisha iyariyo yose, canke\tsinkeneye kuribo yuko bondisha"
  51,58,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tImana\tniyo\tmutanzi\tw’imigisha,\tkandi\tniyo\tnyene ubushobozi bukwiye"
  51,59,"Mu vy’ukuri bamwe bahemukiye imitima yabo bazoba bafise ahandi hantu nkaha bagenzi babo bari, rero ntiba ntware gihuti huti"
  51,60,"Ibihano\tbikaze\tcane\tbizoshikira\tbamwe\tbahakana\tumusi\twabo bemerewe"